;i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:487:"<p>A new meeting card appears on the home page when a meeting begins, providing quick access to recording and meeting prep (“Prep me”) with event context. Users can dismiss it so it won’t reappear for that meeting.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls">https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls</a></p>
