;}}s:13:"last-modified";a:2:{i:0;i:1769583470;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:483:"<p>Assistants now support in-chat Q&A about Day.ai features and workflows, with responses derived from documentation. This is positioned as a way to reduce context-switching while configuring assistants and schedules</p>
