i:1769583291;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:577:"<p>Day.ai now lets assistant schedules deliver outputs to any Slack channel, expanding beyond inbox-only notifications. The change is aimed at making scheduled reports and alerts visible to entire teams without manual forwarding. Configuration is done via the assistant notification setting (‘notify via’).</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls">https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls</a></p>
